claim.claim-text:
1. A material cutting apparatus comprising: 
a feed conveyor; 
a machine tool adjacent to said feed conveyor; 
a shuttle vise movably disposed on said feed conveyor, said shuttle vise being adapted for clamping a workpiece on said feed conveyor when in a clamping position and moving the workpiece to a cutting position adjacent to the machine tool; and 
an adjustable stop on said feed conveyor for adjusting a distance between said stop and said shuttle vise and stopping said shuttle vise at said cutting position.

44. The improvement of claim 40 further comprising; 
a switch; and 
a cam rotatable by said prime mover and having a cam lobe thereon for engaging said switch when said cam is in a predetermined position.
